{"tid":1922105,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美驅逐艦闖南海 華斥「挑釁」","createTime":"2020-03-12T11:16:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T02:41:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"22f6ddf1ef37da0891f80ee7598a222b09cf3634","tid":1922105,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200312/5AO537TWXKBQIFNYA5WD2JHS4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200312%2F5AO537TWXKBQIFNYA5WD2JHS4I%2F&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BF7Oh%2FyAFRgp1rU3tL1w%2BGY%3D&h=2b136043\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200312%2F5AO537TWXKBQIFNYA5WD2JHS4I%2F&h=1cf8fc71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200312/5AO537TWXKBQIFNYA5WD2JHS4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n美驅逐艦闖南海 華斥「挑釁」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200312/large/1583946646_d60a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200312%2Flarge%2F1583946646_d60a.gif&h=c2142cf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國海軍「麥克坎貝爾」號導彈驅逐艦。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍「麥克坎貝爾」號導彈驅逐艦，周二（10日）進入南海西沙海域，繼去年1月後再次在這個有主權爭議的海域執行「航行自由」任務。中國軍方昨搶先美方公佈事件，批評美方的行為「挑釁」和違反國際法規則，解放軍南部戰區組織海空兵力全程對美艦跟蹤監視、查證識別，並予以警告驅離。<br />\n<br />\n第二度執行「航行自由」任務<br />\n<br />\n解放軍南部戰區新聞發言人李華敏表示，美軍「麥克坎貝爾」號擅自闖入中國西沙領海，已遭南部戰區的海空兵力警告驅離。「美方打着『航行自由』的幌子，一而再、再而三地在南海騷肌肉、挑釁滋事。這是違反國際法規則的霸權行徑，是威脅南海地區和平穩定的禍亂之源。」他重申中國對南海諸島及其附近海域擁有主權，將採取一切必要措施堅決捍衞國家主權安全。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍第七艦隊發言人證實，「麥克坎貝爾」號當時在執行「航行自由」任務，反指中國在南中國海的主權聲索不合法：「通過這次行動，美國證明了這些海域超出了中國可以合法聲索的領海範圍，中國對西沙群島周邊的直線基線主張與國際法不符。」<br />\n<br />\n「麥克坎貝爾」號去年1月也曾闖入西沙海域，當時在美國太平洋艦隊發言人證實行動後，中國外交部隨後向美方交涉。新加坡南洋理工大學研究員高瑞連認為，中國先於美國公佈美艦的行動罕見：「這反映了北京目前的政策，強調即使目前正在抗擊冠狀病毒疫情，解放軍仍然時刻準備着應對外界來犯。」<br />\n<br />\n中通社/法新社"},{"pid":"087a871c576f7350f691133d802632de7473c02f","tid":1922105,"uid":285371,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"Sir this way"},{"pid":"4a8fbd281284470304510ba7901e9df688d7d562","tid":1922105,"uid":77092,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c70ab2a6144254e09ec3e62c80da59145a547531","tid":1922105,"uid":55533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/da6bb3/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/d/attachments/day_191117/20191117_c34f978b0b9100f3f88ciHxvw0Pezsjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fda6bb3%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.discuss.com.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_191117%2F20191117_c34f978b0b9100f3f88ciHxvw0Pezsjs.jpg&h=90e74c8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"789f571f902a9ff27f1eaa60141c02d963ccfeee","tid":1922105,"uid":7278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:21:34.000Z","msg":"大霧啲 大霧啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ae9b4eb29631bdb09b9efa6c7974639657d142","tid":1922105,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T11:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/410/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2015/04/22/150422064932_south_china_sea_map_549x549_bbc_nocredit.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fws%2F410%2Famz%2Fworldservice%2Flive%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F2015%2F04%2F22%2F150422064932_south_china_sea_map_549x549_bbc_nocredit.jpg&h=844aa906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你畫撚晒個海佢啦"},{"pid":"0f9f44acec53716b00aa5f22606b114f264439e2","tid":1922105,"uid":35735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"咁你去人哋海域挑釁返佢吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e80dbf5d0d6bc6d84fc254e94ad443eb597f9cf","tid":1922105,"uid":265839,"like":0,"disl